        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Blockchain Promotion Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Commerce to establish the Blockchain Working Group to submit a report to Congress which contains a recommended definition of the distributed ledger technology commonly referred to as blockchain technology, and other specified recommendations regarding this technology. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
